						<lb/>Şühūdu'l-hāl
						<lb/>Mollā <persName facs="#zone_xwf_skq_qqb">Mehmed</persName> MRZAN ʿan kasaba-i <placeName>Kirşevo</placeName>
						<lb/>Mollā <persName facs="#zone_pnj_tkq_qqb">Mehmed</persName> Hāccı Oğlu
						<lb/>Mollā <persName facs="#zone_xpf_5kq_qqb">Sālih</persName> CZMIK
